This sim will store position data for the robots we want to store data for
It will store both initial and final position data
Store meta data in the same row, such as type of robot and the friction level etc
This simulation is fitted to control the size of mover modules while shaking. If the module is a mover, change the size to small if it is in the zone we want to collect the segregator modules into

3 goals in total
1) Central area
2) Between central area and edge
3) Edge
